-- European Central Bank is Said to Be Purchasing Portuguese Government Bonds
-- B y   L u c y   M e a k i n
-- 2012-01-18T14:01:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/european-central-bank-is-said-to-be-purchasing-portuguese-government-bonds.html
The  European Central Bank  bought
Portuguese government bonds, according to three people with
knowledge of the transactions, who asked not to be identified
because the deals are confidential.  A spokesman for the ECB in  Frankfurt  declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
